F\u2014\nOF U. S. VIA F. D. R., \"SATAN BOUND\" JUDAISM,\nCATHOLICISM, AND IMPURE, IMMATURE ASPECTS\nOF PROTESTANTISM, NOT AWAKE TO THE\nCULMINATION OF ITS GRAND HERITAGE\nMARVELOUS, IMPERATIVE CHRIST SUPER.\nSCIENCE MESSIAH MILLENNIUM TO ALL PEOPLES!\n(See RECESSION ON, Page 11)\nRE DEVIL S MOTOR RECESSION\nGOD'S DETROIT TRIBUNE PRESENTS, FROM \"THE\nMAGAZINE OF WALL STREET\" (85c), March 1\n(Detroit Tribune comends this article to its readers).\nLABOR BOSSES\nATTEMPTING TO TYRANNIZE\nOUR ECONOMY\nBy James J. Butler\nEditor's Note: MR. REUTHER'S DEMANDS ARE OUT\nOF-HAND\u2014FOR HE WELL KNOWS\n\u2014THAT TO DATE LABOR HAS RECEIVED FULL\nCOMPENSATION FOR PRODUCTIVITY IN ADDITION\nTO GETTING EVERYTHING THE TRAFFIC WILL BEAR\nOUT OF AUTOMATION, EVEN BEYOND THE POINT OF\nPRODUCTIVITY WITH PAY RAISES ENCROACHING\nAND CUTTING INTO DUALITY OF PRODUCT AS WELL\n(See MOTOR RECESSION, Page 2)\nBRITAIN'S \"WAGES OF SIN\"\n\"AIRLINER RAMS INTO HILL, 35 DIE\"\n\"U. K. PLANE 5 MINUTES FROM GOAL\"\n(Windsor Daily Star, 2/27)\nGOD TO HIS DETROIT TRIBUNE:\nM-Y-T-H-l-C-A-L, BUT TERRIFYING, TRAGIC,\nPATHETIC, MORTAL THOUGHT, ADAM-EVE PHENOM\nENA OF THE NON-CHRIST SCIENTISTS\nPRISONERS OF THE DEVIL EVERY SINGLE ONE,\nOF THE M-Y-T-H-l-C-A-L, DEVILISH, ANTI-CHRIST,\nADAM-EVE, MURDEROUS CAIN, JUDAS, KNAVES\nAND FOOLS' EGO AND PSYCHOLOGY OF ALL\nHUMAN BIRTHS \"THE GHASTLY FARCE OF\nMATERIAL (so-called] EXISTENCE\"\u2014p. 272, C.S.\ntextbook\u2014MY MASTERPIECE, IMPERATIVE FOR \"THE\nHEALING OF THE NATlONS\"\u2014Revelation\u2014APPRE-\nHENSION OF ETERNALLY PERFECT NATIONS,\nCREATION, AND UNIVERSE OF INCORRUPTIBLE\nINVULNERABLE, OMNIPRESENT HEAVEN AND\nETERNAL LIFE\nWJR, TUES., 3 4\u20149:30 P. M.\nDEVIL'S F. D. R. \"NEW DEAL.\" Etc.\nDEMOCRATS, LAST TWO YEARS' CONTROL OF\nCONGRESS, IN OPPOSITION TO HOOVER, SABOTAGING\nOF RECOVERY PROSPECTS, ULTIMATES IN THEIR\nADVICE TO F. D. R. TO REFUSE TO COOPERATE\nWITH HOOVER TO AVERT A BANK HOLIDAY I\nAND NATIONAL ECONOMY RECEIVES A TRAGIC\nBLOW, FROM WHICH, TOGETHER WITH UNEM\nPLOYMENT, IT NEVER FULLY RECOVERED UNTIL\nPEARL HARBOR PUT SOME 9 to 10 MILLION\nTO WORK!\nBUT THE NATIONAL INDEBTEDNESS HAS NEVER\nCEASED TO RISE, WITH GREATER AND GREATER\nFORCE\nF- D. R.'S ALLIANCES WITH THE UNDERWORLDS\nOF THE U. S. AND RUSSIA, AND \"SATAN BOUND\"\nSUPREME COURT OF THAT PERIOD, PASSED\nTHE COMMUNIST-CONCEIVED AND WRITTEN WAGNER\n(See F. D. R.'S \"NEW DEAL,\u201d Page 1!)\nEVANGELIST BILLY GRAHAM, Sun., 3/2,\nOUTSTANDING!\nBIBLE ENEMIES SEVERELY REBUKED\nTHOSE MOUTHPIECES OF THE DEVIL I WHO KEEP\nTHE BIBLE OUT OF OUR FREE PUBLIC SCHOOLS f\nGOD TO HIS DETROIT TRIBUNE:\nTHE U. S. SUPREME COURT GUILTY\u2014\nSERVED THE DEVIL IN INTERFERING WITH THE\nTHE FREEDOM OF COMMUNITIES TO DECIDE ON THE\nUSE OF THE BIBLE IN OUR FREE PUBLIC SCHOOLS!\nC. S. HQ. IN BOSTON ALSO GUILTY!\nWIRE TO REV. BILLY GRAHAM, 33:\n\"YOUR SUNDAY SERMON WAS SUPERB. WE MUST\nOVERTHROW THE DEVIL S TEMPORARY SUCCESS\nVS. THE BIBLES USE IN EDUCATION.\nMORE POWER TO YOU, GOD'S CHOSEN. PLEASE\nSEND ME TWO COPIES.\"\nAndrew Fruehauf, C.S.\n\nMarch 6, 1958\nLETTER TO EVANGELIST BILLY GRAHAM\nMinneapolis, Minnesota\nDear precious friend, Rev. Graham:\nPlease accept God's dictation to yoj and our Detroit\nTribune for next week:\nEVANGELIST BILLY GRAHAM EXPLAINS\n\"WHY I BELIEVE IN THE DEVIL\" I\n\u2014\"This Week Magazine,\" 3/2,\nNew York Tribune and Detroit News\nGOD TO HIS DETROIT TRIBUNE:\nMy dear precious son, Billy:\nAll of your arguments in behalf of the apparent reality\nof devil fall before such Scriptures as John 8:43, 44, where\nin Jesus says: 'Why do ye not believe My speech, even\nbecause you cannot hear My word? Ye are of your father,\nthe devil, and the lusts of your father ye will do. He was a\nmurderer from the beginning WHO ABODE NOT IN THE\nTRUTH BECAUSE THERE IS NO TRUTH IN HIM! WHEN\nHE SPEAKETH A LIE, HE SPEAKETH OF HIS OWN, FOR\nHE IS A LIAR AND THE FATHER OF IT'!\n(See EVANGELIST GRAHAM, Page 11)\n\"POPE'S VIGOR RENEWED AFTER BRUSH\nWITH DEATH\"\n(News, 3/3)\nGOD TO HIS DETROIT TRIBUNE:\nOUR INVINCIBLE, MARVELOUS, CHRlst\nSUPER SCIENCE MESSIAH MILLENNIUM\nTO ALL PEOPLES,\n'MEDICINE/ SAVED THE POPE'S LIFE!\nVIA MY DETROIT TRIBUNE AND MARVELOUS,\nIMPERATIVE CHRIST SCIENCE UNIVERSAL\nMESSIAH THE DEVIL'S MATERIA MEDICA COULD\nNOT HAVE PROLONGED HIS PRESENCE HERE I\nAND THE DEVILISH ERRORS OF R. C. INDIRECTLY\nBROUGHT ABOUT HIS ILLNESS AND THREATENED\nDEPARTURE TO THAT COLLECTIVE CONSCIOUSNESS\nCALLED 'THE NEXT WORLD' WHERE MY\nCHOSEN PEOPLE, CHRISTLIKE CHRISTIAN SCIEN\nTISTS WOULD HAVE TAKEN GOOD CARE OF\nHIM!\nRELAXES TRADITIONAL RULES\n(See POPE'S VIGOR, Page 2)\nBIBLE OF NATIVE OF POSTERITY OF\nJESUS' TIME AND COUNTRY\nMarch 1, 1958\nDr. George M. Lamsa, Founder\nThe Aramaic Bible Society, Inc.\n21 E. 40th Street Room 1004\nNew York 16, N. Y.\nMy dear Dr. Lamsa:\nHow good of you to send me your precious volume,\n\"Holy Bible From The Peshitta,\" \"The authorized Bible of\nthe Church of the East.\" It is doubly precious receiving\nGod s treasure house of wisdom and understanding, divine\nRevelation, from one who has himself authored a modern\ntranslation of the original Aramaic.\n(See BIBLE OF NATIVE, Page 11)\nLABOR'S DAILY\nTO 'FOLD' OR TO SURVIVE?\nIS A PRISONER OF THE DEVIL\nPresents Photos of Skirtless Females\u2014\nPAGAN, ANTI-CHRIST PRACTICE I\u2014 IN CONTEMPT\nOF JESUS' BASIC FACT OF HEALTH, HEALING, AND\nDIVINE GUIDANCE:\nTHE FLESH PROFITETH NOTHING. IT IS THE\nSPIRIT THAT THE WORDS THAT I\nSPEAK UNTO YOU, THEY ARE SPIRIT AND\nTHEY ARE LIFE\" I\u2014John 6:63.\n(See LABOR'S DAILY, Page tl)\nSEN. McNAMARA ON TV. Sun.. 3/2\n\"SATAN BOUND\nTinw*c S Dm EI) THAT E e,senh OWE\u00df ADMINISTRA\nTION S POST-OFFICE PROGRAM FOR EXPANSION\nA PHONY'I COMPLAINS AGAINST THE L-I-A-S\n--l*N GOF NEW POST-OFFICE BUILDINGS 'WE'LL\nNEVER OWN 'EM* I\nGOD'S DETROIT TRIBUNE'S RESPONSE\n'THE POOR FISH'! 'Either' of votes I\nuld co \u2666\u2022\u00abP\u00bbr*r\u00bb 9'aat ,\u00abrn, to buy o\u00bb build,\nrather than rent. 9\n(See SEN. McNAMARA, Page 11)\nTribune\nRepresenting \"Our Father-Mother Oodi\" our Divine Publisher\nCrusader For The Invincible Triumphant Divine Rights of Man\nDETROIT, MICHIGAN, SATURDAY, MARCH TsTi9s3\"\nFEAR NO EVIL\ndhriil\nBy Elizabeth Ellington\n\u201cAnd when Jesus was entered into Capernaum them\ncame unto him a centurian, beseeching him\n\u201cAnd saying, LORD, MY SERVANT LIETH AT HOMF\nSICK OF THE PALSY, GRIEVOUSLY TORMENTED\nScience and Health with Key to the Scriptures by Marv\nBaker Eddy, teaches: y\n\u201cWhen will the error of believing that there is life in\nmatter, and that sin, sickness, and death are creations of\nGod. be unmasked? When will it be understood that matter\nhas neither intelligence, life,\nnor sensation, and that the\nopposite belief is the prolific\nsource of all suffering?\n\"God created all through\nMind, and made all perfect\nand eternal. Where then is\nthe necessity for recreation\nor procreation?\" (Ibid., p.\n205)\nCHRIST JESUS, THE\nESSENTIAL WAY\nChrist Jesus is the essential\nwayshower of our well-being.\nHe is right now serving us\nto show us how to gain and\nmaintain health, happiness,\nand rise above sin, sickness\nand death. However, for us\nto gain and maintain these\nhigh marks, we must strive\nto have that Mind which* was\nin Jesus.\n\"LIFE MORE\nABUNDANTLY\"\nThis one Mind. God. good,\nis conducive to the pursuit\nof happiness, peace, joy anti\n\"JESUITS DEMAND EQUAL FEDERAL AID\nTO CHURCH SCHOOLS\"\n(\"Church and State Monthly Revlifc\"\u2014Mafth)\nGOD TO HIS DETROIT TRIBUNE:\nNO PUBLIC MONEY FOR \"SATAN BOUND\"\nCATHOLICISM, JUDAISM, OR ANY\nProtestant parochial schools i\nTHE ONLY PURE, TRUE RELIGION, THERAPEUTICS,\nAND EDUCATION, CULTURE, POLITICS, ENTERTAIN\nMENT, RECREATION, CONTROL OF 'NATURAL'\nSCIENCE\u2014NATURALLY A PRISONER OF THE DEVIL\n\u2014IS TO BE FOUND IN MY, GOD'S, GREATEST\nAND ONLY PURE AND MATURE, COMPLETE, TRUTH\nREVEALING C-A-U-SE OF ALL TIME\u2014MARVELOUS\nCHRIST SUPER SCIENCE UNIVERSAL MESSIAH \"THE\nPREDESTINED, EVENTUAL, THE ONE AND THE\nONLY RELIGION AND THERAPEUTICS\n(See FEDERAL AID, Page il)\nF. D. R. 'TAKEN' AT YALTA (A.F.. C.S.)\n\"SUICIDE AT THE SUMMIT\"\n\"WHY TOP-IEVEL CONFERENCES ARE\nALWAYS DISASTROUS\"\nSisley Huddleston C'Humen Events/'\n2/24)\nGOD TO HIS DETROIT TRIBUNE:\nWt present Mr. Huddleston's studies not because we\n\u2022re unequivocally opposed to a Summit conference at this\ntime\u2014conferences and negotiations are obviously better\ncc n e W bMt BE YE W,SE AS serpents, AND HARM\nLESS AS DOVES', as Jesus so truly said\nnT\u00b0ucL L^ 0N $F D> R HEBR AIC, R. C., AND\nOTHER NON-CHRIST SCIENTIST DEMOCRATS'\nBLUNDERING AND RACKETEERING I\n..I! Why W# pre4#nt th following from Mr. Huddles\nton s studies:\n(Excerpts reprinted from HUMAN EVENTS 2/24)\nSUICIDE AT THE SUMMIT\ny Top-Level Conferences are Always\nDisastrous\nBy Sisley Huddleston\n\n\u2022jT.h.f.n, Russia, the United Steles end Britain,\nresen e y their top levels, took decisions amid Levan\n(See F. D. R. \"TAKEN,\" Pago 2)\n\"KOHLER PROBE DOUBLE TROUBLE\nFOR GUNACA\"\nGon rr\\ uit (Detroit Times, 3/D\nGOD TO HIS DETROIT TRIBUNE:\nIT IS HIGH TIME THAT\nGOV. WILLIAMS'. REUTHER'S. MAZEY'S\nocr..\u201e CRIMINAL CONSPIRACY\nWE G DOtIn? dc UNACA BE EXP \u00b0SEDII!\nHITLER tftn PERM,T THE TACTICS OF MUSSOLINI,\nMESSUH Vat.!? ,N MY PRE COOS U. S., THE\nAH NATION TO ALL THE NATIONS I\nluvr w?^!!J A BIE hyp \u00b0CRITES I\nHAVE WE NOT A U. S. SUPREME COURT?\n(See KOHLER PROBE, Page 11)\nDETROIT\nI contentment.\nWe can be still and know\nthe Truth. The voice of God\nis whispering into our spirit,\nual hearing that He loves,\nand is sustaining us; our sub\nstance, being of Him; Christ\nI is showing us the way. He is\nlife more abundantly, giving\nus the quantity and quality\nof strength to sustain us and\nincrease our mental capacity\nto carry on His business.\nEXPECT GOOD\nAT ALL TIMES\nIt is through our own spirit\nual expectations that we gain\npower over the material\nsenses. So our opinions\nshould be under the doctrine\nof God: the one and only\nMind: and Christ Jesus, the\nson: of the spiritual nature\nof the Father.\nIn Science and Health, p.\n(Continued on Page 4)","height":"28020","width":"18831"}}
